column1: The leaders at my company keep people informed about what is happening
column2: My manager is a great role model for employees
column3: The leaders at my company have communicated a vision that motivates me
column4: I have access to the things I need to do my job well
column5: I have access to the learning and development I need to do my job well
column6: Most of the systems and processes here support us getting our work done effectively
column7: I know what I need to do to be successful in my role
column8: I receive appropriate recognition when I do good work
column9: Day-to-day decisions here demonstrate that quality and improvement are top priorities
column10: My manager (or someone in management) has shown a genuine interest in my career aspirations
column11: I believe there are good career opportunities for me at this company
column12: This is a great company for me to make a contribution to my development
